s the importance of a more\nnationwide decision-making attitude for the future as the condition of each\nstate depends on the nationwide behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jun 2020 22:13:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 20:41:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-15"}
