lar dynamics. Quorum sensing behavior, characterized by the onset of\ncollective behavior in the intracellular dynamics as the number of cells\nincreases above a threshold, is also studied. Our analysis shows that the cell\npopulation density plays a dual role of triggering and then quenching\nsynchronous oscillations in the intracellular dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Jun 2020 03:59:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-09"}
